---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Contact" description="Contact Shift at Midnight Compass — report errors or provide verified sources.">
  <div class="panel hero" style="padding: 28px;">
    <span class="eyebrow"><span class="dot accent"></span> Contact</span>
    <h1>Contact</h1>
  </div>

  <section class="panel section">
    <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
    <p style="margin-top: 8px;">Use this page to:</p>
    <ul style="margin-top: 8px; padding-left: 20px; display: grid; gap: 6px; color: var(--muted); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6;">
      <li>Report an outdated or incorrect fact (include the source that contradicts it)</li>
      <li>Provide a verifiable official source for something currently in HOLD</li>
      <li>Request a correction to a published claim</li>
    </ul>
    <p style="margin-top: 14px;">Because this is a fast-test site without a database or backend, the fastest way to report an issue is to note the specific URL and claim ID from the page.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="panel section">
    <h2>What to Include</h2>
    <div class="can-card" style="margin-top: 14px;">
      <h3>Useful reports include</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>The page URL and claim ID (if visible)</li>
        <li>The official source that contradicts the published fact</li>
        <li>A link to the official source or a screenshot of the current official page</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="cannot-card" style="margin-top: 12px;">
      <h3>Reports that cannot be acted on</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Anonymous claims without a verifiable source</li>
        <li>Requests to add community guide content or YouTube gameplay answers</li>
        <li>Requests to remove HOLD labels without an official source</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="panel section">
    <h2>Response Time</h2>
    <p style="margin-top: 8px;">This is a one-person operated fast-test site. Corrections will be reviewed against official sources before any change is made. Do not assume a response within a specific timeframe.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="panel section">
    <h2>Disclaimer</h2>
    <p style="margin-top: 8px;">This site does not sell, advertise, or collect user data. Contact messages are not used for any purpose other than responding to the report.</p>
  </section>
</Base>
